description: This Chainlink VRF common Sakura purrs with a rating of 37, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 111, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, Box for East, Nine Lives for South, and 5 for West. Sakura has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/10373-14950-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Sakura [111 Votes, Common]
